comments: In the UK it was released on the Fontana label, but, after reaching #2, it was withdrawn from sale. Gainsbourg arranged a deal with Major Minor Records and on re-release it reached #1, the first banned #1 single in the UK and the first single in a foreign language to top the UK charts. It was also #1 in Austria, Norway and Switzerland.
